columns.name: id
columns.description: The identifier that Amazon Route 53 assigned to the health check.

columns.name: caller_reference
columns.description: A unique string that you specified when you created the health check.

columns.name: health_check_version
columns.description: The version of the health check.

columns.name: linked_service_principal
columns.description: If the health check was created by another service, the service that created the resource.

columns.name: linked_service_description
columns.description: If the health check was created by another service, an configurationtional description that can be provided by the other service.

columns.name: cloud_watch_alarm_configuration
columns.description: A complex type that contains information about the CloudWatch alarm that Amazon Route 53 is monitoring for this health check.

columns.name: health_check_config
columns.description: A complex type that contains detailed information about one health check.

columns.name: health_check_status
columns.description: A list that contains one HealthCheckObservation element for each Amazon Route 53 health checker that is reporting a status about the health check endpoint.
